00:05:14.219 --> 00:05:16.189
If you want her, then go for it

00:05:16.289 --> 00:05:17.425
- Huh? Yeah but,

00:05:17.526 --> 00:05:19.229
I believe it's just like you
said.

00:05:19.329 --> 00:05:20.397
